item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

[quote=“whyprod, post:1, topic:418167”]hey im learning to code other source’s and i wanted to know what is the file type that contains the npc X, Y pots,

i dont want any random npcs i need to know what file the shops and that are in with the x and y cords so i can change please help[/quote]I am assuming you are referring to shop coordinates? That would be the spawn-config file cause the npc itself is the shop generally. You need to look in actionhandler.java to find the shopid is all.
